{"tid":2343062,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"「休刊王」不畫獵人又跑去看別人的漫畫！冨樫義博也狂讚《鬼滅之刃》，「鬼滅之刃真的讓我超喜歡的！」","createTime":"2020-12-27T15:29:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T16:18:18.000Z","uid":6097,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"af5e393efdb21c6e4ef363f3105b02136fd81e3e","tid":2343062,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T15:29:06.000Z","msg":"喜歡《鬼滅之刃》的人可不只是動漫迷！同樣在 Jump 連載《獵人 HUNTER&times;HUNTER》的知名漫畫家冨樫義博，其實早在《鬼滅之刃》播出動畫之前就曾經盛讚這部新作：「希望：絕望≒ 憎惡：愛情，這就是我所會喜歡作品的黃金比率，《鬼滅之刃》真的讓我超喜歡的！」冨樫義博點出了《鬼滅之刃》在希望和絕望、憎恨和愛情之間達到一種巧妙平衡，才會讓這部作品一旦開始看了就停不下來！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/m.juksy.com/archives/amp/94428\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fm.juksy.com%2Farchives%2Famp%2F94428&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd4WZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=cf7ab842\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/m.juksy.com/archives/amp/94428</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iySjQZe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiySjQZe.png&h=e7f674c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45d74f99e35d220d7a90d23cdf1cc036a4a7dbe4","tid":2343062,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T15:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0762c53f061f73b37c90664bd4a21ebc01531e58","tid":2343062,"uid":4574,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T15:37:10.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">在希望和絕望、憎恨和愛情之間達到一種巧妙平衡<br />\n</span><br />\n富堅復刊<br />\n畀我嘅感受"},{"pid":"ad9129b3ca4d0fab2368bdc446fdcd4c40cd46bd","tid":2343062,"uid":108133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0762c53f061f73b37c90664bd4a21ebc01531e58","tid":2343062,"uid":4574,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T15:37:10.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">在希望和絕望、憎恨和愛情之間達到一種巧妙平衡<br />\n</sp